{"THEURGIST":[{"def":"One who pretends to, or is addicted to, theurgy.","pos":""}],"THEURGY":[{"def":"A divine work; a miracle; hence, magic; sorcery.","pos":""},{"def":"A kind of magical science or art developed in Alexandria among the Neoplatonists, and supposed to enable man to influence the will of the gods by means of purification and other sacramental rites.","pos":""}]}